extends layouts/default
block content
  section.home-banner
    .container
      .home-banner__img.aos-init(
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="0"
        data-aos-duration="1500"
        data-aos-offset="-200"
      )
        img(src='images/Logo-workbench.svg' alt loading='lazy')
      .home-banner__title
        h1.aos-init(
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-delay="300"
            data-aos-duration="1000") Our Vision
      .home-banner__subtitle.aos-init(
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="600"
          data-aos-duration="1000") Our vision for the Agency Workbench is simple, to make your life easier!
      .home-banner__text.aos-init(
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="900"
          data-aos-duration="1000") Our vision for the Agency Workbench is simple, to make your life easier! At Mitera, we pride ourselves on being at the forefront of change and innovation in pregnancy risk assessment. We understand that our agency partners juggle many responsibilities to help build families via surrogacy. We have developed the Mitera Agency Workbench to simplify the case management process. Our customized portal offers surrogacy agencies and fertility centers a one-stop-shop to manage scheduling, track screenings, access reports and make payments with ease. Mitera’s frictionless portal makes the gestational carrier screening process seamless, flexible and transparent.
      .home-banner__text.aos-init(
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="900"
          data-aos-duration="1000") The Agency Workbench is a FREE platform that will save time, reduce effort and give your team autonomy. A modern approach to perinatal care.

