  section.home-about
    .container
      <video autoplay="" muted="" loop="" class="home-about__bg-video">
        <source src="images/bg_video_banner.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      </video>
      .home-about__title
        h2.aos-init(
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-delay="300"
            data-aos-duration="1000") What is the Mitera Agency Workbench?
      .home-about__text.aos-init(
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="600"
          data-aos-duration="1000") Obtaining medical records can take over a month of outreach and paperwork. Scheduling screening services and waiting for replies can be overwhelming to manage with many hours of administrative time. The Mitera Agency Workbench simplifies your journey by providing everything you need, all in one place. It is an online platform that streamlines your screening process and offers medical records collection services, maternal-fetal medicine screening service bookings and psychological assessment options. 
      .home-about__info
        .home-about__video
          .surrogacy__heading_video(
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="1000")
            img(src="images/home-pre-video.jpg" alt loading='lazy')
            video(id = "my-video" src="images/video.mp4" preload="auto" muted)
        .home-about__list(
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-duration="1000")
          .home-about__list-title
            h3 How it works? 
          .home-about__list-item
            img(src='images/ic_ul.svg' alt loading='lazy')
            span Simply add a new client, either a gestational carrier candidate or intended parent. 
          .home-about__list-item
            img(src='images/ic_ul.svg' alt loading='lazy')
            span Book services and add-on services in the same timeframe, with no delays. 
          .home-about__list-item
            img(src='images/ic_ul.svg' alt loading='lazy')
            span Access, download or upload reports and records.
          .home-about__list-item
            img(src='images/ic_ul.svg' alt loading='lazy')
            span Register payment details for easy monthly invoicing.
          .home-about__list-item
            img(src='images/ic_ul.svg' alt loading='lazy')
            span Alerts are sent when reports are ready and appointments are coming up! 

